{"tid":1374983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[本地阿拉丁] 屌你老母臭西蕭若元，燈完香港燈台灣","createTime":"2019-07-28T02:43:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T03:11:22.000Z","uid":52658,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5fbcd9bad7c308c84199d36c816f0013ecc12e91","tid":1374983,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:43:39.000Z","msg":"平時都唔撚睇條濕鳩d野<br />\n岩岩見到youtube suggest左呢條友既野比我<br />\n見佢咁岩又講台灣 咪禁入去睇下<br />\n屌你老母越睇越撚火滾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你前幾話警察係琴日唔會開槍<br />\n我信撚左你 衝左出去食撚左幾野<br />\n而家訓撚左係醫院<br />\n呢樣都算喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我屌你老母你講乜撚野蔡英文會贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  又話咩柯文哲唔會選<br />\n屌你老母撚唔知咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但洗唔撚洗經你把西口講出黎<br />\n收下把烏鴉啦死老野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你老母又唔撚知自己廢 <br />\n陣間你真係燈撚死蔡英文 我真係第一個出黎屌你老母臭化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94aaff4e884899c898b8299d15d4b3bd737b1335","tid":1374983,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:11:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}